{"type": "article", "id": 22722, "title": "海牙政府的办公大楼改建，彩色的地毯暗藏了世界名画", "description": "满足开放式办公室设计之余还有荷兰的特色。", "date": "2016-02-23T14:57:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17008, "name": "公共建筑"}, {"id": 997, "name": "政府"}, {"id": 23824, "name": "海牙"}, {"id": 19217, "name": "改建"}, {"id": 23833, "name": "荷兰绘画"}, {"id": 23825, "name": "HofmanDujardin"}, {"id": 23826, "name": "capered architects"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 165, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140632Qr1cUIu6lL4tDONi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>海牙是荷兰南荷兰省的省会，近日重新装修了政府办公大楼。原有的办公大楼包括  Castalia 和 Helicon 两部分，最近一次改建在 1990 年代。Castalia 是由美国著名设计师 Michael Graves （迈克尔·格雷夫斯）在 60 年代的建筑基础上改建的，20 层的红色建筑上有三角形的尖塔，让建筑显得细长。后来用做健康福利和运动（Health, Welfare and Sport）部门。</p>\n<p>而前面的三排较低的建筑 Helicon 是由荷兰建筑事务所 Soeters van Eldonk 加建的，有 14 层，正面呈现出略有错位的阶梯状，同时延续了古典的风格，是社会保障和就业部门（Social Affairs and Employment ）的办公场所。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406156xTDCnI57QZBbuLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4402439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406152xFkRVvnHaiwztgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77317073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Castalia </div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140616VsknAxbL4jBrEqCN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> Helicon</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>新的改建是荷兰政府缩减战略的一部分，同时要改变新的工作方式。荷兰的建筑事务所 capered architects 和 HofmanDujardin 参与其中改建，他们分别负责室外和室内。</p>\n<p>Helicon 和 Castalia 之间的地带原本是绿化的地方，却十分阴暗。改建时就考虑将这里变成明亮开放的交流场所。capered architects 用钢筋搭建一个长 70 米高 20 米的“盒子”，上面覆盖玻璃，让阳光进入这个空间。</p>\n<p class=\"\">此外，他们在中间搭建了一个圆弧型的“桥梁”，它连接两边建筑，充当了新的入口。二楼不忘移植三棵树，以自然的环境来促进交流。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140616a9t3bMwqpgK4RYhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70609756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">改造前</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140617MsSG9pqWdEn6xJQL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41442716\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140617Ydg3DQiVlq8fXJak.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140618tmNnTKX8Mzx3q0IO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140618YOekDqS5UXWugIGj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140619LSiQKtw8Pj9Xf3V5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140620v8LeyS0FYCwoDpVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214062073czDoYnfyWkvjG9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406212CQrpBSuMEwy8G1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406217dKxmCsMGiNRfHXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140622HxAizUnjKmwsLtND.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">在大楼里面，他们增加了图书馆、咖啡馆和会议室等区域，而大面积的玻璃窗也让空间轻盈、透明、开放。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140622V0EHznm4OQLRpq5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406239qXUtlNChygpMLzd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140623b0aKmhDW9VM7fjUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>在修建的过程中，HofmanDujardin 意外地发现原有大厅的天花板和海牙美术馆很类似，地板又像是荷兰 17 世纪的风俗画家 Johannes Vermeer（约翰内斯·维米尔）和 Pieter de Hooch（彼得·德·霍赫）的绘画，带有荷兰古典主义的特征。他们想保留这种风格并扩大到办公室的地毯设计上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140624bSsOvFRlWjrLuDMy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>HofmanDujardin 选用了超过 30 幅关于休闲、健康和工作的绘画，包括梵·高、Jan Toorop、Jan Altink 等荷兰知名画家。他们将绘画扩大到房间的大小，然后划分为50x50 厘米的网格，每一块填充不同的颜色做成地毯，让办公室的室内充满了色彩和个性。<a href=\"http://www.hofmandujardin.nl/de-resident/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">点击这里可以看到每一张地毯和所对应的名画。</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>比如 Castalia 的二楼是一个学习发展中心，玻璃房子里是蓝色调的地毯，它源于梵高的 Amandelbloesem。多层次的蓝色和其他颜色的零星点缀让这个区域格外清凉静谧。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140624tHA9zk5Knj7cwaYd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78537736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140625hdUCVy5FsMuxDm19.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65919811\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140625jdYKiBcy61srk74x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140626mKjPTJB3HYFhilfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89858491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140627dpiLtgMhUIBxn26A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89858491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">梵高的另一幅名画 Korenveld 变化出来的地毯用在了 20 楼的会议室。增加了一份田园式的诗意自然。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021406271zSUrxTBY5qHFsDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81132075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140628bSL0JKRuVrqmpcYw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64858491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140629dtgNbGfLwnHYVTyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.24882075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140629CPXjR3dGHTYBq68D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36674528\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">人物画与此同理，Kees Van Dongen （凡·东根）的 Odalysque Couchee 就用在 15 楼的 Health, Welfare and Sport 部门，这里的画也要反映相关主题。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140630kHtW1fCv2P09qrQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7134434\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140630aCDu7iX8PpZM53lf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64858491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140631KLix2RoWYvXOzD0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64858491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140631Y0jRZXxPQ3HFIOsg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81014151\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>          </p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/782361/de-resident-cepezed-architects-plus-hofmandujardin\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.domusweb.it/en/news/2015/12/31/hofmandujardin_enlarging_dutch_classics.html\">domus</a>、<a href=\"http://www.hofmandujardin.nl/de-resident/\">hofmandujardin</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n\n"}